Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个布阵隐藏着巨大的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 非洲塔周围1000公里的风速数据显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑了殒落情况的部队布局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一部吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento-Mori进入扫射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力供给开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力供给已开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离填充完成还有0187
