Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱分子KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖接受吧 这神之雷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪光与破坏 绝望与苦恼
